    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Trim the woody ends off your<strong> asparagus</strong>, then chop into thirds</p><p>Peel and slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel 2 thin strips of <strong>zest</strong> per person from your <strong>lemon[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>(avoid the white bitter pith)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1692971179379-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
