            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>fresh tagliatelle</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a large pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the taglietelle<strong> </strong>for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the tagliatelle, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1692971187169-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
